title: Heat Vision and Jack
description:
As the result of a NASA miscalculation, Astronaut Jack Austin flew to close to the sun, the rays expanding his mind and making him the smartest man on the planet. Now he and his talking motorcycle (who contains the mind of his former roommate) are on the run from NASA and their assain, actor Ron Silver who want to take his brain. They travel from place to place solving paranormal mysteries with the help of Jack&#039;s newfound ability to become a super genius when his brain absorbs sunlight.

Staring:
Jack Black
Owen Wilson
Ron Silver
